&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13232948" author="jcoveney" created="Mon, 19 Mar 2012 21:52:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 to apply to 0.10 and 0.11 trunk. I tested it and worked fine. My commit credentials aren&apos;t setup yet, so someone else will have to apply/checkin.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For it to apply to 0.10 I had to do:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
